    <item>
      <title>据 Jamuna 电视台报道，尤努斯将领导孟加拉国临时政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/yunus-to-head-bangladesh-s-interim-government-jamuna-tv-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据贾穆纳电视台周二晚间报道，诺贝尔经济学奖得主穆罕默德·尤努斯被任命为孟加拉国军方支持的临时政府首脑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/yunus-to-head-bangladesh-s-interim-government-jamuna-tv-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 18:08:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 绕过大牌人物，转而寻求蒂姆·沃尔兹 (Tim Walz) 的广泛支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/walz-brings-progressive-appeal-as-harris-bypasses-bigger-names</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯的竞选伙伴选择最终在两位州长之间展开——一位承诺将为 2024 年选举提供人口最多的战场，但却有可能疏远重要的党内派系；另一位则是来自可靠蓝州、拥有进步资历的鲜为人知的竞争者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/walz-brings-progressive-appeal-as-harris-bypasses-bigger-names</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 17:26:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国、欧盟批评科索沃关闭塞尔维亚邮局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/us-eu-criticize-kosovo-over-serbian-post-office-closures</link>
      <description><![CDATA[科索沃政府因关闭位于塞族人聚居的北部城市的九个塞尔维亚邮局而受到国际盟友的批评，美国表示对此举“深感失望”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/us-eu-criticize-kosovo-over-serbian-post-office-closures</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 17:05:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国警方警告暴徒，周三将发生更多骚乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/uk-police-warn-rioters-as-more-unrest-planned-for-wednesday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国警方增派了警力，并表示如果极右翼活动分子按照网上流传的计划在周三晚上袭击移民中心，他们准备逮捕数百名极右翼活动分子。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/uk-police-warn-rioters-as-more-unrest-planned-for-wednesday</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 16:53:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>多米尼加修宪旨在遏制独裁统治</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/dominican-constitutional-change-seeks-to-rein-in-autocrats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当拉丁美洲的领导人为了继续掌权而打破宪法任期限制时，多米尼加共和国正在推动改革，使独裁者更难继续执政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/dominican-constitutional-change-seeks-to-rein-in-autocrats</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 16:33:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Williams 首席执行官称国会是建设美国能源项目的关键</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/williams-ceo-says-congress-is-key-to-building-us-energy-projects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[管道运营商威廉姆斯公司的高管表示，对于美国能源项目的建设来说，国会的举措可能比白宫的政策更为重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/williams-ceo-says-congress-is-key-to-building-us-energy-projects</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 16:07:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普封口费法官表示将于下周决定是否回避</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/trump-hush-money-judge-says-he-ll-decide-on-recusal-by-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[审理唐纳德·特朗普封口费案的法官表示，他将于下周决定是否退出这起备受瞩目的案件，前总统在该案中被判犯有 34 项重罪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/trump-hush-money-judge-says-he-ll-decide-on-recusal-by-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 16:00:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
